<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id06588b0c-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s4535"><num value="4535">§ 4535.</num><heading> Regulations</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id06588b0d-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s4535/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> Secretary of the Treasury</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of the Treasury shall prescribe such regulations as may be necessary to carry out this title <ref class="footnoteRef" idref="fn002181">1</ref><note type="footnote" id="fn002181"><num>1</num> See References in Text note below.</note> and the amendments made by this title <ref class="footnoteRef" idref="fn002181">1</ref> (except as provided by subsection (b)).</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id06588b0e-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s4535/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Secretary of Labor</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of Labor shall prescribe such regulations as may be necessary to carry out the labor value content determination under <ref href="/us/usc/t19/s4532">section 4532 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="id06588b0f-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d">(<ref href="/us/pl/116/113/tII/s210">Pub. L. 116–113, title II, § 210</ref>, <date date="2020-01-29">Jan. 29, 2020</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/134/53">134 Stat. 53</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id06588b10-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id06588b11-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="id06588b12-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">This title, referred to in subsec. (a), is title II of <ref href="/us/pl/116/113">Pub. L. 116–113</ref>, <date date="2020-01-29">Jan. 29, 2020</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/134/19">134 Stat. 19</ref>, which enacted this subchapter and amended and enacted provisions set out as notes under several sections within this title. For complete classification of title II to the Code, see Tables.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
